column5: Hello Folks,  I was organizing the tackle and pulled out an old, with rusty hooks little cleo lure, but was surprised to see the back look like this:
Thats awsome,  LOL.  I got a bunch of old ones down at the cottage  that I got to check out now,  never noticed that before.  Talk about 'fish porn'  RED
Dude, she's hot!
Ya, it's been a while since they produced those ones.
Nice lure!!! Does she smell like fish right outta the box?
Nothing like a little side boob action.
^^^   I'd hate to loose that lure...

I was at an outpost fishing camp with my son (who was 13 years old at the time) and he snaged a lure on a leader.... It was one of these!.  You could imagine how wide his eyes were when bourght this up and saw it!
Things have changed since those days...now she could be a "little Leo"
Here's the story behind it, taken from a Field & Stream article:
I have 2 in the tackle box. And im afraid to loose them
Nice lure!!! Does she smell like fish right outta the box?
BAHAHAHAHAHAHAH!  Now THATS funny!!!
LOL - so this isn't something I ought to be chucking eh
I have a few for safe keeping. Might be worth something one day.
I have one but I don't use it for fear of losing it....
There's a few on ebay by the looks of it.  Will have to see how high the auction goes.
Nice lure!!! Does she smell like fish right outta the box? Nah man you got to work her a lil bit first.
Hahaha, clever. Thats a good one
Auction in ebay ended.  Not looking like they're worth too much  http://www.ebay.ca/itm/111309405138?ssPageName=STRK:MEWAX:IT&_trksid=p3984.m1423.l2649
